{"tid":1718080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底200萬和理非要死幾多人先肯三罷？","createTime":"2019-11-13T18:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T18:32:28.000Z","uid":234195,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a02ff8e634a6ac0fd55fb428c2a9bfbd753775ad","tid":1718080,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:21:56.000Z","msg":"當初我以為如果真係發展到有人死，一定會真暴動或者真罷工，點知d人都係繼續返工。和理非可唔可以唔好咁自私？手足幫你擋子彈俾人拉俾人打，宜家有人犧牲埋啦！如何一開始和理非肯三罷，根本就唔會有咁多被捕手足同逝世。我唔係話想割席，但真心一問，到底要死幾多人先肯罷工？份工係咪重要過手足條命？我明白長期罷工係要籌備，但宜家日日都有手足重傷啊！和理非可唔可以比d決心同覺悟，加快罷工啊！宜家每日都係用手足嘅血去頂住咋！"},{"pid":"2f38118a3ab2e7f7eeb4014d1ccd4f9d8784f9fa","tid":1718080,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:22:19.000Z","msg":"幾時真三罷啊？"},{"pid":"e366d5c6e6ffbe9d953509024d238e5619583667","tid":1718080,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:22:47.000Z","msg":"到底仲要犧牲幾多人嘅生命同未來"},{"pid":"60f53e490399c8c11263d58eb438954161bd9d81","tid":1718080,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:23:11.000Z","msg":"真三罷！"},{"pid":"f7d085746a6cfb004bde54ca127821bed679a30a","tid":1718080,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:23:33.000Z","msg":"真係唔想再有手足犧牲啦"},{"pid":"04ceaebc0629583fbaad90b27d9b3dc07e6e5a0f","tid":1718080,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"人命黎㗎！"},{"pid":"1024459ed68733cf26fc99cf03a21fe788730a26","tid":1718080,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PYeGuDG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPYeGuDG.jpg&h=036e828b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGt79DH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGt79DH.jpg&h=659a1aec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBrmuDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h